OL,3,C'A seismic change': Inside the lab
OL,4,Cdeveloping a new obesity pill
OL,6,FITV News Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,7,FBarry visits a lab where scientists
OL,8,Fare working on the "next generation"
OL,9,Fof obesity treatments
OL,11,FScientists developing a drug-free
OL,12,Fweight loss pill have told ITV News
OL,13,Fthe UK is on the verge of "a seismic
OL,14,Fchange" in the treatment of obesity.
OL,16,FITV News has been given exclusive
OL,17,Faccess to a laboratory in Oxfordshire
OL,18,Fwhere scientists are developing a non-
OL,19,Fpharmacological alternative to so-
OL,20,Fcalled "skinny jabs", like Mounjaro
OL,21,Fand Wegovy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
