FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780049133
OL,3,C'A seismic change': Inside the lab
OL,4,Cdeveloping a new obesity pill
OL,6,FWhile weight loss injections have been
OL,7,Fdescribed as a "game-changer" for the
OL,8,FUK's obesity crisis, their
OL,9,Favailability on the NHS is restricted,
OL,10,Fthey are expensive to get privately
OL,11,Fand they can cause side-effects.
OL,13,FSirona, developed by Oxford Medical
OL,14,FProducts, looks like a pill but is not
OL,15,Fa medication.
OL,17,FIt's made of hydrogel, a highly
OL,18,Fabsorbent sponge-like material, which
OL,19,Fis also used to make contact lenses
OL,20,Fand some skincare products.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
