FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780049133
OL,3,C'A seismic change': Inside the lab
OL,4,Cdeveloping a new obesity pill
OL,6,FWhen swallowed, the pill expands,
OL,7,Freducing the available volume in the
OL,8,Fstomach, suppressing appetite, leading
OL,9,Fto weight loss. It remains in the
OL,10,Fstomach for several days, before
OL,11,Fbreaking down and passing naturally.
OL,13,F"We are just on the precipice of what
OL,14,Fwe're going to see - a seismic change
OL,15,Fin the way that people interact with
OL,16,Ftheir weight," Dr Camilla Easter, the
OL,17,Fchief executive officer of Oxford
OL,18,FMedical Products told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780049133
OL,3,C'A seismic change': Inside the lab
OL,4,Cdeveloping a new obesity pill
OL,6,F"It's not about the aesthetics, it's
OL,7,Fabout the other diseases that obesity
OL,8,Fcan cause. We need more interventions
OL,9,Flike Sirona, so that we don't have to
OL,10,Fget to a point that people are living
OL,11,Fwith obesity at all. That is where we
OL,12,Fshould be aiming as a society."
OL,14,FIn clinical trials of Sirona,
OL,15,Fparticipants lost an average of 4.4%
OL,16,Fof their total body weight over 24
OL,17,Fweeks, consuming almost 400 fewer
OL,18,Fcalories a day.
OL,20,FSirona is now awaiting regulatory
OL,21,Fapproval in Europe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
