OL,3,C'A seismic change': Inside the lab
OL,4,Cdeveloping a new obesity pill
OL,6,FRuth Harding, from Gloucestershire,
OL,7,Fhad an allergic reaction when she
OL,8,Ftried weight loss injections.
OL,10,FBut, after years of trying to lose
OL,11,Fweight, she lost three stone in six
OL,12,Fmonths when she took part in the
OL,13,Fclinical trial for Sirona.
OL,15,F"It was just fantastic because this
OL,16,Fwas something that worked for me,
OL,17,Fexactly how the GLP-1s seem to be
OL,18,Fworking for other people," she told
OL,19,FITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780049133
OL,3,C'A seismic change': Inside the lab
OL,4,Cdeveloping a new obesity pill
OL,6,F"If I can get the same effect without
OL,7,Fthat chemical input - then it's a win
OL,8,Fwin."
OL,10,FThe developers believe Sirona could
OL,11,Fhelp people who are overweight, but
OL,12,Fnot yet at a BMI eligible for weight
OL,13,Floss drugs, to prevent them
OL,14,Fprogressing into obesity.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
