OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780049133
OL,3,C'A seismic change': Inside the lab
OL,4,Cdeveloping a new obesity pill
OL,6,FTo qualify for Mounjaro (tirzepatide)
OL,7,Fon the NHS, patients must have a Body
OL,8,FMass Index (BMI) of at least 40 and
OL,9,Fhave weight-related health conditions
OL,10,Flike Type 2 diabetes, high blood
OL,11,Fpressure, heart disease or sleep
OL,12,Fapnoea.
OL,14,FOxford Medical Products believe Sirona
OL,15,Fcould also benefit people who want to
OL,16,Ftransition off drugs like Wegovy or
OL,17,FMounjaro, to prevent them regaining
OL,18,Fweight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
