PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780049133
OL,3,C'A seismic change': Inside the lab
OL,4,Cdeveloping a new obesity pill
OL,6,FExperts say Sirona is one of many
OL,7,Fweight loss innovations on the
OL,8,Fhorizon, including pills from the
OL,9,Fmakers of both Wegovy and Mounjaro,
OL,10,Fwhich are currently awaiting approval
OL,11,Fin the UK.
OL,13,F"The opportunity is right here with
OL,14,Fthis new wave of innovations," said
OL,15,FProfessor Amira Guirguis, Chief
OL,16,FScientist at the Royal College of
OL,17,FPharmacy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780049133
OL,3,C'A seismic change': Inside the lab
OL,4,Cdeveloping a new obesity pill
OL,6,F"But these treatments are not a quick
OL,7,Ffix, these treatments need to be part
OL,8,Fof a holistic treatment pathway,
OL,9,Fincluding psychological, lifestyle and
OL,10,Fexercise interventions."
OL,12,FIn the months ahead, Sirona could be
OL,13,Fjust one of several significant
OL,14,Fbreakthroughs in the treatment of
OL,15,Fobesity - a disease that affects
OL,16,Faround a quarter of UK adults.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
